name: Vessels 184: ‘The Shark’
description: Tony is a born gambler.  He is good at it too.  A regular at Dutch’s place, and a dangerous player, many a toff has lost a fortune going toe to toe with old Tony.  Lady Luck is always with him.  People mistake this to be a figurative statement but in Tony’s case he actually has a gun in his jacket that he calls ‘Lady Luck’.  She does not often miss...
